РђфIt's me.

432
00:23:50.333 --> 00:23:51.791
РђфYou can come back home.

433
00:23:52.291 --> 00:23:54.541
РђфI'll nurse you back to health.

434
00:23:55.541 --> 00:23:57.625
РђфBut only on one condition.

435
00:23:58.958 --> 00:24:01.750
РђфYou need to stop
Рђфwith your promiscuous lifestyle.

436
00:24:02.416 --> 00:24:03.583
РђфStopРђд

437
00:24:04.500 --> 00:24:05.666
Рђфlying.

438
00:24:06.541 --> 00:24:08.541
Рђф-Do you hear me?
Рђф-[heart monitor continues]

439
00:24:14.875 --> 00:24:18.875
РђфFrom Monday to Thursday.
Рђфwe know what we'll cook for him.

440
00:24:19.416 --> 00:24:24.541
РђфI'm thinking that maybe
Рђфon Fridays we cook him soup.

441
00:24:24.625 --> 00:24:27.166
РђфAnd then on the side.
Рђфhe'll have some fruit.

442
00:24:27.250 --> 00:24:29.708
РђфObviously. we'll have to puree them.

443
00:24:29.791 --> 00:24:31.041
РђфYes. ma'am.

444
00:24:31.125 --> 00:24:36.333
РђфUh. I'm sure he'll be feeling better
Рђфby the end of the week. ma'am.

445
00:24:37.208 --> 00:24:38.208
Рђф[chuckles]

446
00:24:39.083 --> 00:24:40.458
РђфThank you. Ntombi.

447
00:24:40.541 --> 00:24:41.625
РђфYes. ma'am.

448
00:24:42.458 --> 00:24:44.041
Рђф[siren wailing]

449
00:24:47.750 --> 00:24:49.125
Рђф[Joyce] Trust me.

450
00:24:50.291 --> 00:24:52.708
Рђфmy children are
Рђфthe only reason why I'm here.

451
00:24:52.791 --> 00:24:53.833
Рђф[Magesh] Yeah.

452
00:24:56.583 --> 00:24:57.833
РђфMagesh.

453
00:24:59.500 --> 00:25:00.833
Рђф-[Magesh] And now?
Рђф-Oh. my God.

454
00:25:03.458 --> 00:25:05.291
Рђф-[groans]
Рђф-No. no. no.

455
00:25:05.375 --> 00:25:06.541
Рђф-Essie. Essie.
Рђф-It can't be.

456
00:25:06.625 --> 00:25:08.875
Рђф-What's going on. Magesh? Where is Jonasi?
Рђф-Essie. Essie. [shushes]

457
00:25:08.958 --> 00:25:10.041
РђфPlease. calm down.

458
00:25:10.125 --> 00:25:11.916
РђфLet's not jump to conclusions.

459
00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:13.375
Рђф-Maybe they've moved him.
Рђф-[sighs]

460
00:25:13.458 --> 00:25:14.791
РђфLet's just wait for the doctor.

461
00:25:14.875 --> 00:25:19.125
РђфDoctor. please. can you tell me
Рђфwhat happened to my husband?

462
00:25:19.833 --> 00:25:23.625
РђфUh. Mr. Gomora was discharged
Рђфearlier this morning.

463
00:25:23.708 --> 00:25:24.791
РђфHuh?

464
00:25:24.875 --> 00:25:30.083
РђфHe was signed out by Ms. Lindani Mbatha.

465
00:25:30.166 --> 00:25:31.291
Рђф[gasps]

466
00:25:32.583 --> 00:25:33.750
Рђф-You see now?
Рђф-Huh?

467
00:25:33.833 --> 00:25:35.333
РђфYou see. Gesh?

468
00:25:35.416 --> 00:25:37.291
РђфHe's chosen to go die in that dump.

469
00:25:37.375 --> 00:25:38.875
Рђф[scoffs] Whatever.

470
00:25:38.958 --> 00:25:40.916
РђфNo. no. no. I'm done now.

471
00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:42.458
РђфI am done with Jonasi.

472
00:25:42.541 --> 00:25:45.708
РђфHim and I will see each other
Рђфon the day of his funeral.

473
00:25:45.791 --> 00:25:47.416
РђфFinished. End of story.

474
00:25:47.500 --> 00:25:49.375
Рђф-Calm down--
Рђф-No. no. no.

475
00:25:49.458 --> 00:25:50.625
Рђф[tense music playing]

476
00:25:51.791 --> 00:25:53.125
РђфLet's all calm down.

477
00:25:55.833 --> 00:25:56.833
РђфYeah.
